main event: A civilian reported a sighting of a cigar-shaped unidentified flying object in Nederland, Texas on February 6, 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed for 5 to 10 minutes,The cigar-shaped object was approximately 7 feet in size, The sighting occurred at dusk with high overcast conditions, The object was very bright and emitted noticeable lights, The conclusion of the investigation was that the object remained unidentified.
witness description: a civilian whose identity is redacted
